{"title_page": "Janet Mathews (Janet Chethipuzha)", "text_new": "\n\n\n{{more references|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name = Janet Mathews\n| image = \n| image_size = \n|caption     = JANET MATHEWS (Janet Chethipuzha) \n|birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|2006|07|21}}\n| birth_place = [[Switzerland]]\n| nationality = Switzerland\n| occupation = Singer & Dancer\n| parents = \n|spouse        = \n|partner       =\n|children      =\n}}\n\n'''Janet Mathews'''<ref name=\"garshomonline\">{{cite web|url=https://www.garshomonline.com/janet2017/|website=garshomonline.com|title=Janet Mathews Switzerland: Garshom Young Talent Award 2017 &lsaquo; :: Garshom ::|accessdate=2020-04-01}}</ref> is a singer and a dancer, born and raised in Switzerland. She entered the world of music and dance at the age of three.\n\n==Early life==\nMathews was born in the city of [[Olten, Switzerland]], in 2006 to Cibi and Jincy Chethipuzha. She has two brothers called Joel and Jones. By the age of ten, she had recorded more than 10 album songs and has performed several dance shows. Mathew's first commercial song was on the Christian devotional album ''Paithal''.\n\n==Awards==\n*[[Garshom Awards|Garshom International Award]]- Young Talent 2017\n*Kalaratna 2017, [[Keli]] International Kalamela<ref name=\"keliswiss\">{{cite web|url=http://www.keliswiss.org/|website=keliswiss.org|title=www.keliswiss.org/|accessdate=2020-04-01}}</ref>\n*Winner [[Thaikkudam Bridge]] Song Challenge 2017\n*Winner Bharatanatyam reality show Naatiyatharagai 2017 @ [[IBC Channel 13|IBC Channel]] London\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|1}}\n\n== External links ==\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mathews, Janet}}\n[[Category:2006 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n{{Switzerland-singer-stub}}\n", "text_old": "\n\n\n{{more references|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name = Janet Mathews\n| image = \n| image_size = \n|caption     = JANET MATHEWS (Janet Chethipuzha) \n|birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|2006|07|21}}\n| birth_place = [[Switzerland]]\n| nationality = Switzerland\n| occupation = Singer & Dancer\n| parents = \n|spouse        = \n|partner       =\n|children      =\n}}\n\n'''Janet Mathews'''<ref name=\"garshomonline\">{{cite web|url=https://www.garshomonline.com/janet2017/|website=garshomonline.com|title=Janet Mathews Switzerland: Garshom Young Talent Award 2017 &lsaquo; :: Garshom ::|accessdate=2020-04-01}}</ref> is a singer and a dancer, born and raised in Switzerland. She entered the world of music and dance at the age of three.\n\n==Early life==\nMathews was born in the city of [[Olten, Switzerland]], in 2006 to Cibi and Jincy Chethipuzha. She has two brothers called Joel and Jones. By the age of ten, she had recorded more than 10 album songs and has performed several dance shows. Mathew's first commercial song was on the Christian devotional album ''Paithal''.\n\n==Awards==\n*Garshom Young Talent Award 2017, [[Garshom Awards|Garshom International Awards]]\n*Kalaratna 2017, [[Keli]] International Kalamela<ref name=\"keliswiss\">{{cite web|url=http://www.keliswiss.org/|website=keliswiss.org|title=www.keliswiss.org/|accessdate=2020-04-01}}</ref>\n*Winner [[Thaikkudam Bridge]] Song Challenge 2017\n*Winner Bharatanatyam reality show Naatiyatharagai 2017 @ [[IBC Channel 13|IBC Channel]] London\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|1}}\n\n== External links ==\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mathews, Janet}}\n[[Category:2006 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n{{Switzerland-singer-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Pauljins", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eAwards", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Janet_Mathews_(Janet_Chethipuzha)"}
